{"tid":1502881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問胡椒球係咪過鳩咗期","createTime":"2019-08-24T18:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T18:15:32.000Z","uid":306337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65965816d06a03b3b08ec285797ce52851025c96","tid":1502881,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:10:48.000Z","msg":"小弟今日走俾人兜背射咗好多下落條頸同耳到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時洗完就冇咁燒同痛。<br />\n今日呢隻我4點半中 㷫到而家<br />\n沖咗兩次涼 淋咗幾次鹽水<br />\n而家冰敷緊,<br />\n都係feel到條頸燒緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打feel the same<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 聽日睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係一位前線巴打,有一個心願想大家幫幫我...<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dHsatT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dHsatT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借位推我嘅一個小心願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n睇到呢到 幫我推下唔過份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d450212120205d4a85bca2ce784ae701b22aabf0","tid":1502881,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:11:23.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d3470dfb12969d0dbc9b0d58a648bb218f21c97f","tid":1502881,"uid":14830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e21e02088d78a5f44017aeb8d1c4a8d5e34e0e","tid":1502881,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3470dfb12969d0dbc9b0d58a648bb218f21c97f","tid":1502881,"uid":14830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci